&lt;h2 id="cargo-install-troubleshooting">Cargo install troubleshooting&lt;/h2>
&lt;p>cargo로 뭐 설치하려고 할 때&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-gdscript3" data-lang="gdscript3">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="ln"> 1&lt;/span>&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="n">PS&lt;/span> &lt;span class="n">D&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>\&lt;span class="n">dev&lt;/span>\&lt;span class="n">rust&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">&amp;gt;&lt;/span> &lt;span class="n">rustup&lt;/span> &lt;span class="n">update&lt;/span>
